---
title: Organic Beef & Pepper Mac & Cheese with a Crispy Panko Topping
description: Mac and cheese just got a flavorful makeover that’s got heads turning. This Tex-Mex twist on a classic is all about Southwestern flair: lightly charred green pepper, roasted garlic, diced tomato, and four kinds of cheese add serious oomph to the creamy sauce. This super savory melange coats corkscrew cavatappi, then is sprinkled with a layer of crispy panko. Beautiful!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6407513fef95911f810723a7-4d8bffd5.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/6526f30cbfc560dc00ea4ff3.pdf
